# Function row
# Fn+F3 -> lock ?
# Fn+F4 -> XF86Sleep
# Fn+F5 -> Wifi-toggle
# Fn+F6 -> XF86WebCam
# Fn+F7 -> XF86Display
# Fn+F8 -> XF86MonBrightnessDown
# Fn+F9 -> XF86MonBrightnessUp
